---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout title="Business" description="Founder notes, market curiosity, product judgment, and company-building interests from Dipak Wani.">
  <section class="page-intro">
    <p class="eyebrow">Company building</p>
    <h1>Founder intent, shown through work.</h1>
    <p class="lede">I am interested in markets where applied intelligence changes how serious people work: AI products, knowledge systems, finance, research tools, and products with unusually high taste.</p>
  </section>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="split">
      <article class="panel">
        <p class="eyebrow">Markets I am studying</p>
        <h3>Applied intelligence</h3>
        <p>Where models become workflows, and workflows become durable products with real distribution.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="panel">
        <p class="eyebrow">Product judgment</p>
        <h3>What makes a product excellent</h3>
        <p>Clarity, timing, taste, switching cost, trust, and a sharp understanding of the user’s real constraint.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="panel">
        <p class="eyebrow">Company notes</p>
        <h3>What makes a market attractive</h3>
        <p>Urgent pain, frequent use, budget, differentiated access, distribution insight, and room for compounding advantage.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="panel">
        <p class="eyebrow">Founder path</p>
        <h3>Former cofounder experience</h3>
        <p>Previous company-building experience informs how I think about product, customer pain, teams, and operating tempo.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-head">
      <div><p class="eyebrow">Reach out</p><h2>For serious builders.</h2></div>
      <p>For founders, investors, researchers, and builders: reach out if you are working on AI products, applied intelligence, knowledge systems, finance, or tools for serious builders.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="actions">
      <a class="button" href="mailto:blog@dipakwani.com">Contact</a>
      <a class="button secondary" href="/work/">See work</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
